HEADWORD: Chalcographist
<hw>Chal*cog"ra*phist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>An
engraver on copper or brass; hence, an engraver of copper plates for
printing upon paper.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

